Name: Sabine Mueller
Position: CEO DHL Consulting, EVP
Data: How do you get more diversity in the C-suite? By fixing corporate culture – not people. Too often, women’s leadership development programs send the message that women need to ‘fix’ themselves in order to be ready for a senior role. I have gone through these coaching programs myself. I’ve been taught how to sit, how to stand, and how to adjust my voice in order to be successful.Here’s what I know now: Developing good leaders is not about fixing them. It’s about building a new work culture that fosters a variety of leadership styles in which diverse racial, ethnic, and gender identities are considered as professional as the prevailing model.In fact, the future depends on it. Time and again, leadership diversity is shown to be a critical success factor in a company’s economic performance. Yet, there’s been a frustrating lack of diversity progress in German companies. The share of women sitting on DAX 40 company boards is just 17%. It’s not just about gender either. There’s also little to no representation from individuals of differing social or cultural origins, sexual orientations, gender identities, or physical ability.Here are my three key recommendations to focus on fixing corporate culture and letting people flourish. Let me know what you think in the comments!#FutureofWork#DEandI#Diversity#Leadership#WomenAtWork#ConversationsForChange#leadership#personaldevelopment#womenenmpoweringwomen#womenleaders#womenwholead#womenwhoinspire#womeninleadership#diversityandinclusion

Data: ISO 14001: 2015 is an environmental management standard that is universally accepted.► Here's what you can know from the blog to help you set=up a seamless EMS process:1️⃣ What is an environmental management system?2️⃣ Advantages of ISO 14001 Certification3️⃣ How does the standard work?One of the most significant advantages of establishing an EMS is the reputation of being one of the few companies that care enough to lessen their ecological consequences.This may improve your company’s ties with consumers, the general public, and the general public, but it also has additional advantages.In addition to a positive media persona, many businesses may save money by using a sustainability policy.This can be accomplished by lowering the number of accidents that result in liability expenses and obtaining insurance at a lower rate.#esg#iso14001#ems#sustainability#sustainabledevelopment

Data: We bootstrapped RocketChart from 0 to an Exit in less than 2 years 🔥 Here's the complete journey – full transparency – including insights, mistakes, failures & successes 🥰To be honest, launching a (bootstrapped) business is tough.You feel lonely. Alone with your decisions and their consequences.You have to do everything on your own to get that idea out of the ground 🥵Because you believe in it so strongly, you are ready to pull those roots out of the ground.Whatever it takes.Always keeping an eye on your bank account 😰But it's also a super fun and rewarding experience!You learn so much about yourself, about humans ✨About what you are ready to accept and lose.You experiment by doing and failing.You learn to take a step back 🧘🏼‍♂️To ignore those who want to see you fall.You learn about what truly matters to you.And you have the chance to meet awesome people 😊This article is the next episode of our journey bootstrapping RocketChart.
